short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add search engine provider Handy Tab Search

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Handy Tab Search enhances your browser by integrating its specialized search engine. Search results and advertisements are provided by trusted partners, ensuring a seamless and secure browsing experience through HTTP redirects.

By clicking "Add to Chrome" you agree to install the "Handy Tab Search" extension, set Handy Tab Search as your default search engine in Chrome, and accept the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

For more information, please visit:
- Privacy Policy: https://tryhandytab.com/helps/priv.html
- Terms of Use: https://tryhandytab.com/helps/term.html
- About: https://tryhandytab.com/helps/about.html
- Contact: https://tryhandytab.com/helps/contacts.html
